  "notes": [
    "This study examined ethnic disparities in male breast cancer between Han and Mongolian populations in Inner Mongolia, China",
    "The study found minimal ethnic disparities in disease burden and healthcare utilization, but identified economic factors as important predictors",
    "Sample size limitations particularly affected the Mongolian patient subgroup analysis"
